Description: Avance Gas Holding Ltd. is a Bermuda-based company that is engaged in the transportation of liquefied petroleum gas (LPG). The Company is an owner and operator of very large gas carriers (VLGCs). Avance Gas provides LPG transportation services to destinations in Europe, South America, India and Asia, mainly loading the Middle East Gulf and the United States Gulf/United States East Coast. The Company operates a fleet of approximately 14 ships and over four dual-fuel new buildings. The Company's fleet of vessels includes Iris Glory, Venus Glory, Promise, Mistral (scrubber), Monsoon (scrubber), Breeze (scrubber), Passat (scrubber), Sirocco (scrubber), Levant (scrubber), Chinook, Pampero, Avance Polaris (LPG dual fuel), Avance Capella (LPG dual fuel), Avance Rigel (LPG dual fuel), Avance Avior (LPG dual fuel) and NB Dual-Fuel TBN (LPG dual fuel).
